WEBVTT

00:00:01.169 --> 00:00:04.570
Jehovah is on my side.

00:00:04.570 --> 00:00:08.089
I will not be afraid."

00:00:08.089 --> 00:00:14.449
One of the most encouraging expressions in God's inspired word, Jehovah is on my side.

00:00:14.449 --> 00:00:17.329
It reminds me when I was growing up in school.

00:00:17.329 --> 00:00:22.649
We would pick teams in the playground to play basketball or other sports, and two students

00:00:22.649 --> 00:00:27.609
would be selected as captains, and then they would begin picking alternating back and forth

00:00:27.609 --> 00:00:29.929
to make up their team.

00:00:29.929 --> 00:00:34.530
One of the captains was usually more skilled than the other, and you always wanted to be

00:00:34.530 --> 00:00:36.729
on his team.

00:00:36.729 --> 00:00:40.049
If you were picked on his team, that was a good day.

00:00:40.049 --> 00:00:41.850
Life was good.

00:00:41.850 --> 00:00:48.210
Well our scripture today is telling us that we have Jehovah on our side.

00:00:48.210 --> 00:00:49.929
We are on his team.

00:00:49.929 --> 00:00:53.810
That guarantees victory, success.

00:00:53.810 --> 00:00:55.810
We cannot lose.

00:00:55.810 --> 00:01:01.729
We have many beautiful examples in the Bible of those who were victorious with Jehovah

00:01:01.729 --> 00:01:03.210
on their side.

00:01:03.210 --> 00:01:10.409
David facing Goliath, exciting and resounding victory.

00:01:10.409 --> 00:01:11.409
But what about other victories?

00:01:11.409 --> 00:01:15.730
What about Stephen facing the mob that stoned him to death?

00:01:15.730 --> 00:01:23.650
It may not seem to be a victory at the moment, but where is Stephen now?

00:01:23.650 --> 00:01:28.819
A incredible victory for him.

00:01:28.819 --> 00:01:35.700
Well this is the result of Jehovah's promise at Isaiah 54, verse 17.

00:01:35.700 --> 00:01:39.140
Isaiah 54, verse 17, just the first part of the verse there.

00:01:39.140 --> 00:01:41.459
So comforting.

00:01:41.459 --> 00:01:47.459
No weapon formed against you will have any success.

00:01:47.459 --> 00:01:50.459
So we keep Jehovah on our side.

00:01:50.459 --> 00:01:52.060
We win.

00:01:52.060 --> 00:01:57.379
Unfortunately though, we don't always feel like that winner.

00:01:57.379 --> 00:02:03.780
For some of us, it might happen when we have to wait for Jehovah to answer our prayer.

00:02:03.780 --> 00:02:08.139
We might become impatient, begin to wonder if even heard our prayer.

00:02:08.139 --> 00:02:09.740
Is he still on my side?

00:02:09.740 --> 00:02:12.180
Where is his attention elsewhere?

00:02:12.180 --> 00:02:15.819
Or perhaps it's not that we doubt Jehovah being on our side.

00:02:15.819 --> 00:02:18.300
We have complete confidence in him.

00:02:18.300 --> 00:02:25.219
But when we're awaiting an answer for our prayers, we have laid out our situation before

00:02:25.219 --> 00:02:27.580
Jehovah.

00:02:27.580 --> 00:02:30.979
Now we're waiting to discern his answer.

00:02:30.979 --> 00:02:36.219
And maybe that's not as clear to us as we wish it would be or thought it would be.

00:02:36.219 --> 00:02:39.139
We begin to have doubts.

00:02:39.139 --> 00:02:42.419
Are we even able to recognize his answer?

00:02:42.419 --> 00:02:48.500
We begin to lose confidence not in Jehovah, but in ourselves, in our discerning his help.

00:02:48.500 --> 00:02:50.300
So what can help us?

00:02:50.300 --> 00:02:57.300
Well, we need to remind ourselves that Jehovah has a bigger picture and perceives things

00:02:57.300 --> 00:03:00.060
that obviously we don't see.

00:03:00.060 --> 00:03:05.419
We need to keep a spiritual outlook on life and to stay focused on what's really, truly

00:03:05.419 --> 00:03:07.659
matters.

00:03:07.659 --> 00:03:15.409
When we're caught up in the moment of the anxiety, it begins to look like we're losing.

00:03:15.409 --> 00:03:21.210
But even then, Jehovah remains on our side.

00:03:21.210 --> 00:03:24.090
He's looking down the path further than we are.

00:03:24.090 --> 00:03:27.210
He sees the victory.

00:03:27.210 --> 00:03:30.210
So what's the lesson for us?

00:03:30.210 --> 00:03:35.409
We need to just calm down and wait on Jehovah.

00:03:35.409 --> 00:03:38.569
The victory is guaranteed.

00:03:38.569 --> 00:03:44.129
And other times, it may seem that we just, as it were, cannot get out of our own way.

00:03:44.129 --> 00:03:46.289
