00:03:46.289 --> 00:03:47.770
We're imperfect.

00:03:47.770 --> 00:03:54.729
We have a health crisis or time and unforeseen circumstances devastates us.

00:03:54.729 --> 00:03:57.810
At those moments, it seems like we're losing.

00:03:57.810 --> 00:04:02.729
But wait, wait, Jehovah is still on our side.

00:04:02.729 --> 00:04:05.969
He is not looking at the score today as it were.

00:04:05.969 --> 00:04:11.129
